description:
## Bug Report

After https://github.com/pingcap/tidb/pull/60848, the follow error message can not be redacted

### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)

```sql
set session tidb_redact_log = on;
use test;
create table t (c int);
insert into t values (1),(1);
alter table t add unique index i(c);
set global tidb_cloud_storage_uri = 's3://global-sort';
alter table t add unique index i(c);
```

### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)

> ERROR 1062 (23000): Duplicate entry '?' for key 't.i'

### 3. What did you see instead (Required)

> ERROR 1105 (HY000): found index conflict records in table t, index name is 't.i', unique key is '[1]', primary key is '2'

### 4. What is your TiDB version? (Required)

<!-- Paste the output of SELECT tidb_version() -->

https://github.com/pingcap/tidb/commit/c71ebaf73ed9620745f327ad147f27fc06d73297
